        Executes basic processing of asynchronous task. This method will always be invoked on a background thread; no UI modifications should be attempted from this method, but should instead be performed in the lambdas/interface implementations specified to BaseFluentAsyncTask.setProgressListener(ProgressListener), BaseFluentAsyncTask.setSuccessListener(ResultListener), and BaseFluentAsyncTask.setFailureListener(ResultListener).
